Why are you following me?

66
00:06:04,930 --> 00:06:07,940
Ran told me to follow you.

67
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:11,020
She's worried because of what the jobs are about.

68
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:13,650
If you're near a track when you get paid,

69
00:06:13,650 --> 00:06:17,360
you might spend all of it like always.

70
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:20,450
Don't worry.

71
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:25,160
This time I'm earning triple the money.

72
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:31,750
Are you sure you should've accepted the same job three times?

73
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:34,250
He's the most popular horse right now.

74
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:36,920
Coincidences happen.

75
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,130
I meant as a detective.

76
00:06:39,130 --> 00:06:41,430
That's him!

77
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,640
White Spirits,

78
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:50,850
"White Spirits, Racing Horse" -the horse with the pure white soul.

79
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:56,530
"Yasutaka Hase (40), Trainer"

80
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,740
It's a beautiful horse.

81
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:05,830
No wonder they say he's the horse of the decade.

82
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:08,450
Indeed, indeed.

83
00:07:08,450 --> 00:07:12,040
I've been blessed as a horse owner.

84
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,040
Who are you?

85
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,750
Please excuse me.

86
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,630
I took your call earlier.

87
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,630
"Kozo Tokuyoshi (55), Horse Owner" -I'm Kozo Tokuyoshi.

88
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:24,140
You must be Kogoro Mouri, the great detective.

89
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:27,430
Indeed, I am the great detective, Mouri.

90
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:32,230
I see. So you're the owner of that amazing horse.

91
00:07:32,230 --> 00:07:36,860
You said you were here about White Spirits?

92
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,940
Indeed.

93
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:42,950
Tokuyoshi, I understand you've been receiving death threats

94
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:47,240
