95
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:49,450
How do you know that?

96
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:53,250
Detectives are bound to confidentiality,

97
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,830
so I cannot answer your question,

98
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:58,840
