100
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,260
By three different people, too.

101
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:09,060
I see. That's perfect, then.

102
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,060
What?

103
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:12,440
I'd like to hire you, too.

104
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:15,940
Please protect White Spirits, Mouri.

105
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:17,020
What?

106
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:19,860
He's been hired by four people now.

107
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:25,530
Thank you, Mouri.

108
00:08:27,450 --> 00:08:28,660
The next day,

109
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:33,620
White Spirits was being transported to a track outside Tokyo

110
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:36,960
to participate in a commemorative race.

111
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:39,460
"White Spirits"

112
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,760
We're counting on you.

113
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:44,760
"Masao Shiomi (50), Horse Trailer Driver" -Got it.

114
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:49,930
Why are you here, too, Ran?

115
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:52,350
I'm watching you.

116
00:08:52,350 --> 00:08:55,140
I wasn't sure Conan could handle it alone.

117
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:58,360
You're unbelievable.

118
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:02,440
Just kidding. I'm actually a White Spirits fan.

119
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:05,030
What? Don't tell me you...

120
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:08,530
Of course not. I'm underage.

121
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:14,250
I just like how fast and beautiful White Spirits is.

122
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:16,250
That's why I'm worried.

123
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:18,460
Yeah, but...

124
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:20,750
Why not, Mouri?

125
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:23,050
I feel safer with more people.

126
00:09:23,050 --> 00:09:24,420
Come, miss.

127
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:27,840
You're welcome to join me in my car.

128
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,550
Thank you!

129
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:37,650
Don't do this, sir. This is reckless.

130
00:09:37,650 --> 00:09:40,650
If something were to happen to White Spirits...

131
