Don't worry.

132
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:47,030
The great detective Kogoro Mouri is here.

133
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:50,240
White Spirits will appear in the race as planned.

134
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:53,240
You all just need to do your jobs.

135
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,960
You all?

136
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,220
What's up with that car?

137
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:21,940
They shouldn't surprise people like that.

138
00:10:21,940 --> 00:10:25,150
Hey, wasn't that this person?

139
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:27,240
"This Month's Woman Jockey White Spirits' Rider"

140
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,450
"Chizuru Kakuta (25), Jockey"

141
00:10:29,450 --> 00:10:30,820
They're on schedule.

142
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:37,540
That's them.

143
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:39,750
