They said to tell him, "Head to OND3BRG."

244
00:17:32,221 --> 00:17:35,808
OND3? BRG?

245
00:17:35,808 --> 00:17:37,893
Where is that?

246
00:17:40,104 --> 00:17:41,814
BRG...

247
00:17:41,814 --> 00:17:47,403
If it's an abbreviation like before, BRG...

248
00:17:47,403 --> 00:17:49,113
Bridge.

249
00:17:49,113 --> 00:17:51,281
Maybe it's a bridge.

250
00:17:51,281 --> 00:17:56,537
So OND3 is the name of the bridge?

251
00:17:56,537 --> 00:17:59,998
OND... OND...

252
00:17:59,998 --> 00:18:03,419
If that's an abbreviation, too, then...

253
00:18:06,422 --> 00:18:08,090
Hey, look.

254
00:18:08,090 --> 00:18:09,216
Up there.

255
00:18:11,009 --> 00:18:14,221
OND3. Onodera Overpass 3.

256
00:18:14,221 --> 00:18:17,808
"Onodera Overpass 3"

257
00:18:31,447 --> 00:18:32,489
Could it be?

258
00:18:48,088 --> 00:18:50,507
Darn it. I can't see from here.

