I still can't see it.

261
00:19:01,810 --> 00:19:03,312
Here should be good enough.

262
00:19:04,396 --> 00:19:06,398
I see it.

263
00:19:06,398 --> 00:19:07,483
Stake it out.

264
00:19:07,483 --> 00:19:08,484
Yes, sir.

265
00:19:25,209 --> 00:19:29,296
Darn. It's been thirty minutes.

266
00:19:29,296 --> 00:19:31,256
What's going on?

267
00:19:32,382 --> 00:19:35,302
Could it be? Chiba, Takagi.

268
00:19:35,302 --> 00:19:36,303
Yes.

269
00:19:42,726 --> 00:19:44,520
What is this?

270
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:45,604
What happened?

271
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:49,608
It's not here!

272
00:19:49,608 --> 00:19:51,527
What?

273
00:19:51,527 --> 00:19:53,820
Darn it! They got us!

